    "description": {
      "content": "The Ultimate Debian Database (UDD) gathers Debian package, bug, Lintian, popcon, and reproducibility data into a single SQL database. UDD exposes web tools and JSON exports (such as the bugs-search and maintainer dashboards) at udd.debian.org rather than a single formal REST API.",
